g] ||  1972  || ''Faith and Practice'' || [https://web.archive.org/web/20110727133539/http://www.npym.org/fnp/faith_practice.html 1993 (Second ed.) ''Faith and Practice''] (undergoing revision) [https://web.archive.org/web/20141019171106/http://www.npym.org/sites/default/files/F%2BP%20transitional%207-2014.pdf July 2014 Transitional Edition (111 pdfs)] [https://www.npym.org/sites/default/files/NPYM%20F%26P%20-%20March%202018.pdf 2017 ed. Faith & Practice (303 pdfs)]\n|-\n|  [http://www.pacificyearlymeeting.org/ Pacific Yearly Meeting]  ||  1947  || ''Faith and Practice'' || 1952, 1957, 1963, 1973, 1985, [http://pacificyearlymeeting.org/fp/index.html 2001 (revision of the 1985 edition)]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pacificyearlymeeting.org/faith-and-practice/ |title=Faith and Practice |publisher=Pacific Yearly Meeting |date=20 June 2014 |accessdate=19 September 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pacificyearlymeeting.org/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/PYMFandP2001secure.pdf |title=Faith and Practice |publisher=Pacificyearlymeeting.org |accessdate=20 September 2015}}</ref> Revision of the 2001 F&P started in 2014 and is ongoing.<ref>https://www.pacificyearlymeeting.org/committee-newsletters-and-reports/faith-and-practice-revision/</ref>\n|-\n! Individual Meetings !! Meeting Formed !! Title !! Year of Adoption\n|-\n|  Cliftondale Friends Christian Church ([[Ulster County, New York|Ulster County, NY]]) || 1801 || ''Book of Discipline Containing the Faith and Practice'' || [https://web.archive.org/web/20100901001515/http://www.clintondalefriends.org/THE%20BOOK%20OF%20DISCIPLINE2.htm 1996 with revisions through 2006]\n|-\n|  [[Fairhope, Alabama]] Friends Meeting (an independent Conservative meeting) || 1970 ||''Discipline of Fairhope (Alabama) Friends Meeting 1970''.|| [http://www.quakerinfo.com/fairhopemmfp.pdf 1970 ''Discipline of Fairhope (Alabama) Friends Meeting'' (18 pdfs)]\n|-\n|  Freedom Friends (Salem, OR) || ||''Faith and Practice''|| [http://freedomfriends.org/FF-What.htm Feb. 2009]\n|-\n| [[Meeting House of the Friends Meeting of Washington|Friends Meeting of Washington, DC]]  ||  before 2013 || ''Handbook of Practices and Procedures''  ||  [http://quakersdc.org/Handbook2013 2013 Handbook]\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[Meeting for Sufferings]]\n* \n* [[Query (Quaker)]]\n* [[Recorded Minister]]\n* The [[Religious Society of Friends#testimonies|Testimonies]] of the [[Religious Society of Friends]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|colwidth=30em}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLgkB8soHoOliykI-2TgR2vIYuWTB7hA4W Advices and Queries Videos Youtube Playlist]  Reading of the complete text of \"Advices and Queries\" from the British ''Quaker faith & practice: the book of Christian discipline of the Yearly Meeting of the Religious Society of Friends (Quakers) in Britain'' approved in 1994 with corrections and revisions 1995\u20132008.  A downloadable and printable [http://qfp.quaker.org.uk/chapter/1/ text] is available.  The actual text used begins on pdf 2.  (42 videos, total running time: 21 mins, 21 secs.) Playlists of the same videos for individual days of the week (six videos each): [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLgkB8soHoOljJrDgdgDRjmutUF8mzlujt First Day (Sunday) Advice and Queries] (3 minutes, 3 seconds), [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLgkB8soHoOliUOLLdpdV88hK_LFUa1hTG Second Day (Monday) Advice and Queries] (3 minutes, 17 seconds), [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLgkB8soHoOlh39SIlBmf544tYVDQwuHGV Third Day (Tuesday) Advice and Queries] (3 minutes, 56 seconds), [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLgkB8soHoOljNMVH1hQdPJEThSzdwbXAs Fourth Day (Wednesday) Advice and Queries] (2 minutes, 47 seconds), [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLgkB8soHoOli4IsBMawOfbuvmZeMwZQD1 Fifth Day (Thursday) Advice and Queries] (2 minutes, 55 seconds), [https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLgkB8soHoOlhCbfQLHEiMRarWeNqw8zM3 Sixth Day (Friday) Advice and Queries] (2 minut